# Format: ProjectName|/absolute/local/path|git_url|branches
#
# git_url column is optional:
#   - Leave empty      → local repo only (must already be cloned)
#   - https:// URL     → public repo, or private with GITHUB_TOKEN in .env
#   - git@github.com   → private repo via SSH (key must be loaded)
#
# branches column is optional:
#   - Leave empty      → defaults to main,master,develop,dev (uses whichever exist)
#   - Comma-separated  → only those branches are included in reports
#
LocalOnly|/home/user/projects/local-project||
PublicRepo|/home/user/projects/public|https://github.com/octocat/Hello-World|
PrivateHTTPS|/home/user/projects/private|https://github.com/user/private-repo|main,develop
PrivateSSH|/home/user/projects/ssh-project|git@github.com:user/private-repo.git|main
